WEBVTT

00:03.494 --> 00:04.537
Ooh!

00:04.625 --> 00:06.591
Getting a jump
on the Halloween decorations?

00:06.679 --> 00:08.367
The 'ween dec.

00:08.476 --> 00:11.639
Never. This is from
the window display of my novel,

00:11.727 --> 00:13.376
"A Case of
a Knife to the Brain."

00:13.463 --> 00:14.604
Mm.

00:14.721 --> 00:17.823
You know, we never did do
that book tour across America.

00:17.971 --> 00:20.128
We should do a road trip
when Eddie gets back.

00:20.230 --> 00:22.284
We haven't done one
since we moved down here.

00:22.372 --> 00:23.753
♪ I saw the sign ♪

00:23.966 --> 00:27.534
♪ And it opened up my eyes,
I saw the sign ♪

00:27.622 --> 00:29.362
I'm fine if that was
the last one.

00:29.450 --> 00:30.853
Hey!

00:30.940 --> 00:32.950
Eddie sent us
an e-mail from Taiwan!

00:33.067 --> 00:35.024
From an Internet café.

00:35.111 --> 00:37.160
Oh, man, those babies
are the future.

00:37.247 --> 00:38.557
I bet 10 years from now,

00:38.645 --> 00:40.457
there's two of them
for every Blockbuster.

00:40.567 --> 00:42.365
Print the e-mail
so we can read it.

00:46.403 --> 00:47.972
Here it comes.

00:52.098 --> 00:54.043
"What up, other Huangs.

00:54.130 --> 00:56.489
Taiwan is do-ope.

00:56.715 --> 00:58.768
All the unique
customs..."

01:01.229 --> 01:03.545
"...the Qing dynasty
architecture..."

01:04.873 --> 01:06.397
"...enchanting."

01:06.498 --> 01:09.399
"And don't worry. I'm playing
things safe and smart."

01:09.487 --> 01:10.597
I got this, chief.

01:16.624 --> 01:18.873
Unh! Ugh!

01:19.089 --> 01:20.092
Uggh!

01:20.180 --> 01:22.571
"See you in a few weeks.
Peace out."

01:22.660 --> 01:25.459
And then he drew a skull
out of commas and semicolons.

01:25.547 --> 01:26.775
It's quite good.

01:26.862 --> 01:28.374
Eddie's really getting
our money's worth

01:28.461 --> 01:29.584
out of cultural exchange.

01:29.672 --> 01:31.061
I can't wait
till I get to go.

01:31.149 --> 01:32.948
He had me at
"Qing dynasty architecture."

01:33.078 --> 01:34.617
I'm gonna go hit
the Brittanicas.

01:37.055 --> 01:38.789
We raised some good kids.

01:38.877 --> 01:40.030
We have.

01:40.118 --> 01:42.225
Captions by VITAC...
